 Create a Product List with Prices and Total Calculation
Create a form that includes:
An input field for the product name.
An input field for the product price.
A submit button.
When the form is submitted:
Create a new table row (<tr>) containing the product name and price.
Append the row to a table that lists all the products.
Add a Total Price at the bottom that calculates and updates whenever a new product is added.
